    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长西波隆认为，尽管工资上涨，但仍有迅速削减开支的空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/ecb-has-room-to-cut-swiftly-despite-wage-rebound-cipollone-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执行委员会成员皮耶罗·西波隆 (Piero Cipollone) 表示，即使工人的工资大幅上涨以应对两年来的通胀上升，欧洲央行也可能能够“迅速”降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/ecb-has-room-to-cut-swiftly-despite-wage-rebound-cipollone-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 09:36:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
